Package: COCLIBRARY
Title: Charting Library
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: person("Stephen", "Holzman", email = "stephen@chartsoncharts.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: COCLIBRARY is a charting library API designed to produce publication quality charts according to a style guide as easily as base charting functiongs. The main COCLIBRARY package should be used as a dependency to a custom rolled R package. The custom package only includes a list variable that stores style choices like fonts, margins, color schemes, etc that are referenced by the various charting functions in COCLIBRARY.
Depends: R (>= 3.1.3), ggplot2, grid, png
License: MIT
LazyData: true
